transcript.text: Blind Shipment Feature Blind shipment is generally used by print brokers.
They take orders from their clients, placed order on website and at shipping time.
They put ship from addresses for their convenient.
We have enabled this feature also.
Admin can charge for this facility.
Blind shipping option is available for all.
It can be set for only retailer, only corporate and both retailer and corporate clients.
Admin can charge amount from print brokers for this facility at front end.
This feature will be visible at checkout page and print broker can put ship from addresses for their need.
If you have any queries please contact us at support at on printshop.com.
